General.Name: Atrum Coal NL
General.Description: Atrum Coal Limited explores for and develops metallurgical coal properties. It primarily offers coking coal for steel industry. The company's flagship asset is the 100%-owned Elan Hard coking coal project located in the Crowsnest Pass area of southern Alberta, Canada. It also explores for anthracite in British Columbia, Canada. Atrum Coal Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
